        <abstract> 
<p>Asks JM to send <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> to G. Boccardo in Italy.</p>  
<p>Sends title (suggested by Lyell) for translation of Fritz Müller’s <hi rend="italic">Für Darwin</hi> (which Dallas is translating). CD does not wish to go to great expense in advertising it.</p> 
